LatexCommand citep
key "10.1257/0022051041409075,https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1756-2171.2006.tb00067.x,10.1257/jel.48.4.935,reimers2021digitization"
literal "false"

\end_inset

.
 In smallholder agriculture,
 
