\begin_layout Standard
The rest of this paper is organized as follows.
 Section 2 presents the conceptual framework.
 Section 3 describes the experimental design.
 Section 4 outlines the empirical strategy.
 Section 5 describes the data.
 Section 6 presents the results,
 and Section 7 concludes.
\end_layout

