 The rating dimensions capture attributes that farmers attend to when purchasing and using seed,
 as identified through prior qualitative work,
 including workshops with experts from MAAIF,
 NARO,
 USTA,
 UNADA,
 Naseco Seed Company,
 and extension specialists.
\end_layout

