\begin_layout Standard
We present standard orthogonality tables with pre-registered variables to assess baseline comparability between treatment and control groups.
 For farmer-level outcomes (Table 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "balance_farmer"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"
nolink "false"

\end_inset

),
 no comparison is significant;
 for agro-dealer-level outcomes (Table 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "balance_dealer"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"
nolink "false"

\end_inset

),
 two of 17 comparisons are significant at the 10% level.
 Joint F-tests further confirm baseline balance.
\end_layout

