\begin_layout Subsubsection
Moral hazard and agro-dealer responses
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
Agro-dealers’ practices
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Another alternative explanation for the treatment effects is that the intervention reduces moral hazard among agro-dealers.
 By increasing market transparency and competitive pressure,
 the intervention may incentivize agro-dealers to improve practices that affect seed performance.
